Objective:
1. Write the adventure game plot
2. Code the introduction of the scenario the player is put in
3. Give the player a few choices
4. Depending on what the player chose, give them a new scenario that continues the story
5. Continue this process until the story ends

Pseudocode
Write print statement that explains game to player
Write print statement that introduces the choices the player can make
Take in an input from the player
Write conditional that tests for what the player inputted
    Write print statement that explains new scenario depending on player input